multimedia/sickbeard includes an RC script:
%%PREFIX%%/etc/rc.d/sickbeard

TO START SICKBEARD ON BOOT:
echo 'sickbeard_enable="YES"' >> /etc/rc.conf

START MANUALLY:
%%PREFIX%%/etc/rc.d/sickbeard start

Once started, visit the following to configure:
http://localhost:8081/

